@page "/"

<PageTitle>Sleep Tracker</PageTitle>

<h1>Child Sleep Factors</h1>

<AuthorizeView>
    <Authorized>
        <p>
            Track your child's daily factors and analyze what affects their sleep quality.
        </p>

        <ul>
            <li>Use <strong>Add Daily Factors</strong> to save meals (pranzo, merenda, cena with ingredients), single factors (naps, conflicts, bath, incidents), and sleep quality for each day.</li>
            <li>Use <strong>Results &amp; Ranking</strong> to view single-factor risk rankings, combined-factor pairs, and excluded factors (those tied to good sleep).</li>
            <li>Factors associated with good sleep are automatically excluded from the risk ranking.</li>
        </ul>
    </Authorized>
    <NotAuthorized>
        <p class="lead">
            Welcome to Sleep Factors Tracker. Please login to get started.
        </p>

        <div class="alert alert-info">
            This app helps track factors that may affect your child's sleep and provides analysis to identify patterns.
        </div>

        <div>
            <a href="/login" class="btn btn-primary">Login</a>
        </div>
    </NotAuthorized>
</AuthorizeView>
